Description: project-aware Japanese input method for Grimodex and Fcitx5
 fcitx5-grimodex is a standalone Japanese input method derived from Hazkey.
 It consumes Grimodex project dictionaries and local conversion conditions
 while keeping per-input-context sessions isolated.
 .
 The package uses its own addon, input method, server, settings, runtime,
 configuration, and data identities so it can be installed alongside Hazkey.
